headline: DexCom (DXCM) Surpasses Q3 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: DexCom (DXCM) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +7.02% and +2.72%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
